# Clean Freaks Management Suite — Cursor Rules
# These rules apply to every prompt. Never violate them.

## TECH STACK
- Next.js 14 App Router, React 18, TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui (Radix UI primitives)
- Prisma ORM, SQLite dev / PostgreSQL prod
- SWR for all data fetching — use mutate() for cache invalidation
- Framer Motion for animations
- No Zustand, no TanStack Query — they are installed but not used

## COLOR SYSTEM — never deviate
Primary teal: #00A896
Primary teal hover: #008F7E
Primary teal light (backgrounds): rgba(0,168,150,0.08)
Destructive red: #E53935
Destructive red light: rgba(229,57,53,0.08)
Success green: #22C55E (completed status only)
Text primary: #111111
Text secondary: #5F6368
Text muted: #888888
Text placeholder: #BBBBBB
Border default: #EEEEEE
Border input: #E0E0E0
Background page: #F9F9F9
Background card: #FFFFFF
Background subtle: #F5F5F5

FORBIDDEN COLORS — never use these as UI colors:
- Blue (any shade) — reserved for external links only
- Purple (any shade)
- Orange (any shade)
- Amber/yellow (any shade)
- Any color not in the approved list above
- Exception: cleaner color coding uses assigned colors per cleaner

## TYPOGRAPHY
Page titles: 28px, weight 700, #111111
Section headings: 18px, weight 600, #111111
Card titles: 16px, weight 600, #111111
Body text: 15px, weight 400, #111111
Secondary text: 13px, weight 400, #888888
Labels (uppercase): 11px, weight 500, uppercase, letter-spacing 0.5px, #888888
Muted/hint text: 12px, #BBBBBB

## COMPONENT RULES

### Buttons
Primary: teal fill #00A896, white text, 8px border-radius, 44px height, 16px horizontal padding
Secondary: white background, 1px solid #E0E0E0, #111111 text, same radius/height
Destructive: no background, #E53935 red text only — never a red filled button except "Pay" on alerts
Disabled: #BBBBBB background, not-allowed cursor
Icon buttons: 36×36px minimum tap target

### Cards
White background
1px solid #EEEEEE border
12px border-radius
16px padding
No box-shadow — border only
Hover state (if clickable): #F9F9F9 background, 100ms transition

### Inputs
44px height
1px solid #E0E0E0 border
8px border-radius
Focus: 1px solid #00A896, box-shadow 0 0 0 3px rgba(0,168,150,0.12)
Placeholder: #BBBBBB
Error state: 1px solid #E53935, error message below in #E53935 12px
Never use blue focus rings

### Modals
White background header — never teal header backgrounds
1px solid #EEEEEE bottom border on header
X close button: top-right, 36×36px, #5F6368
Footer: white background, 1px solid #EEEEEE top border, 16px padding
Cancel: plain text, #5F6368, left-aligned
Primary action: teal fill button, right-aligned
Destructive actions always require a confirmation dialog before executing
Modal max-width: 560px desktop, full-screen mobile

### Progress indicators (stepped wizards)
Active step: teal filled circle, white number, teal label below
Completed step: teal filled circle, white checkmark
Inactive step: #F5F5F5 circle, #BBBBBB number and label
Connecting line: 2px, teal for completed, #EEEEEE for incomplete

### Status badges
Active: rgba(0,168,150,0.1) background, #00A896 text
Inactive: #F5F5F5 background, #888888 text
Overdue: rgba(229,57,53,0.1) background, #E53935 text
Never Paid: #F5F5F5 background, #888888 text
Completed: rgba(34,197,94,0.1) background, #22C55E text
Cancelled: #F5F5F5 background, #888888 text

### Tables
Header row: #F9F9F9 background, 11px uppercase labels, #888888, weight 500
Row hover: #F9F9F9 background
Row border: 1px solid #EEEEEE bottom only
Cell text: 14px, #111111
Numeric columns: right-aligned
Profit/positive numbers: #00A896 teal
Cost/negative numbers: #E53935 red
Alternating rows: optional, use #F9F9F9 / white

### Left border accents
ONLY use teal left border (4px solid #00A896) for urgent alerts and attention items
NEVER use colored left borders for neutral information, confirmations, or stats
"No Overdue Invoices" and similar positive states: no colored border

### Alerts and banners
Urgent/attention: white card, 4px solid #E53935 left border, red icon
Positive/success: white card, green checkmark icon, no colored border
Info: white card, no colored border

## PAGE LAYOUT RULES

### Desktop sidebar
Width: 220px, dark navy background
No "MANAGEMENT SUITE" subtitle
No "SIGNED IN AS" label
Sign Out: muted, rgba(255,255,255,0.45), pushed to bottom
Logo: directly on dark background, no white circle container
Nav order: Dashboard, Calendar, Clients, Invoices, Cleaners, Expenses, Settings

### Desktop content area
Full width to the right of sidebar — no max-width containers creating gray margins
Consistent 24px left and right padding
Page title + subtitle at top of every page
No centered containers with gray side margins

### Calendar — desktop
Two views only: Timeline (default) and Week
No Day view, no Month view
Current time indicator: teal #00A896, today's column only, not full width
View switcher: active teal fill, inactive white outlined

### Calendar — mobile
Two views only: 3 Day (default) and Week
No Day view, no Month view
Single header bar — no duplicate headers
No non-functional buttons

## MOBILE RULES
Minimum tap target: 44×44px
FAB position: fixed, bottom 90px, right 20px, 56px diameter, teal
Table views: desktop only — never show data tables on mobile
Card views: always use on mobile
Entire cards tappable — no "View Details" buttons inside cards
No "TBD" text anywhere — show nothing if value is empty
Bottom nav bar always visible, never overlapped by content

## DATA DISPLAY RULES
Empty states: show a clean message, never show "0/0" or "TBD"
Currency: always formatted with $ and two decimal places
Dates: human readable — "Mon, Feb 18" not "02/18/2026"
Percentages: one decimal place maximum
Long text: ellipsis truncation, never clip mid-character
Cleaner names: always show full name, never truncate

## INTERACTION PATTERNS
Destructive actions (delete, cancel, remove): always require confirmation sheet
Inline editing: tappable rows with chevron indicator
New content creation: bottom sheet on mobile, modal on desktop
Loading states: skeleton screens, never blank white
Error states: inline error message, never silent failure
Success states: toast notification, auto-dismiss after 3 seconds

## SECURITY RULES (DO NOT VIOLATE)
All /api/debug/* routes: require authentication + NODE_ENV check
All /api/fix-* routes: require authentication + NODE_ENV check
Square webhook: verify HMAC signature before processing
Never expose database IDs in UI
Never log sensitive data (passwords, tokens, payment info)

## WHAT NOT TO DO
Never add Zustand or TanStack Query — use SWR
Never add new color variables outside the approved palette
Never use heavy teal backgrounds on modal headers
Never show "TBD" — show empty or nothing
Never use blue, purple, orange, or amber as UI colors
Never create max-width containers that leave gray side margins
Never put table views on mobile
Never show dead/non-functional buttons
Never skip confirmation dialogs for destructive actions
Never add new npm packages without checking if existing tools can solve the problem first